        Protocol GET /observation?cpr=&intervalstart=&codelist& codesystem= where is in a UNIX timestamp in milliseconds , e.g, 123414701 and where is in the JSON format |c1|c2|...|cn| where ci is a valid code according to the codesystem. and where could be UIPAC or another supported system.
